      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. so if the rebar is what handles the tension, what happens if the rebars aren't placed correctly or if there's a gap in the reinforcement? does the concrete just fail immediately or is there some kind of internal way it tries to compensate?",
      "source": "evaluator"
